People ex rel. Edison Electric Light Co., Appellant, v. Wemple, Comptroller, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 25, 1891.)

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Mayham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion of attorney general denied. Motion of relator to-amend by restoring further sum of $67.40 granted. For opinion on appeal* see 15 N. Y. Supp. 711.
